空难造成三人遇难，遇难的三人均为江山中学赴美游学的女学生：王琳佳、叶梦圆、刘易芃，其中刘易芃在空难发生七天后抢救无效在医院身亡。<ref name="xinmin0" />两人事发时坐在飞机的尾部，机尾断裂后被甩出<ref>{{cite web|title=美旧金山警察局正调查叶梦圆被碾前是否活着|url=http://www.cnr.cn/gundong/201307/t20130711_513027031.shtml|author=钱江晚报|publisher=中国广播网|accessdate=2013-07-11|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308072546/http://www.cnr.cn/gundong/201307/t20130711_513027031.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。死者都是在机外找到的<ref name=c08evacuate/>。王琳佳因未系安全带，当场遇难；叶梦圆在医院伤重不治；刘易芃病情危重，7月12日抢救无效死亡。<ref>{{cite web|title=空难一遇难女孩疑遭救护车碾轧 一人未系安全带|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2013/07-09/5017234.shtml|author=北京晨报|publisher=中国新闻网|accessdate=2013-07-11|archive-date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108213742/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2013/07-09/5017234.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国旧金山验尸官罗伯特当地时间2013年7月18日认定，在韩亚航空客机坠机事件中遇难的16岁中国女孩叶梦圆在彈出飛機後，遭趕往現場救災的消防車輾斃，她在空难时没有受到任何致命伤。<ref>{{cite web|title=韩亚航空空难疑遭碾压死者尸检报告推迟公布|url=http://news.163.com/13/0709/14/93BLIUL30001121M.html|author=新闻晚报|publisher=网易新闻|accessdate=2013-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130714125014/http://news.163.com/13/0709/14/93BLIUL30001121M.html|archive-date=2013-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=韩亚空难疑遭碾轧中国女孩身份确认为叶梦圆|url=http://news.163.com/13/0711/01/93FF6RMF00014JB6.html|publisher=网易新聞|accessdate=2013-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130715033412/http://news.163.com/13/0711/01/93FF6RMF00014JB6.html|archive-date=2013-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=韩亚空难中一名中国学生确认死于汽车撞击|url=http://news.cntv.cn/2013/07/20/ARTI1374263424482575.shtml|author=中国新闻网|publisher=中国新闻网|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2018-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112181522/http://news.cntv.cn/2013/07/20/ARTI1374263424482575.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=叶梦圆遭碾轧前曾被误判死亡|url=http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/777kejizhuihui/content-3/detail_2013_07/29/28005359_0.shtml|author=凤凰网|publisher=凤凰网|accessdate=2013-07-29|archive-date=2018-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181112101454/http://news.ifeng.com/world/special/777kejizhuihui/content-3/detail_2013_07/29/28005359_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=美确认韩亚空难1遇难女生遭救护车碾压至少一次|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-07/13/c_125002567.htm|author=环球网|publisher=新华网|accessdate=2013-07-13|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221211306/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-07/13/c_125002567.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是旧金山市政府2014年1月29日发布的报告称，叶梦圆在空难后被弹出飞机即死亡，并非先前法医所说的死于救援消防车碾轧，从而直接否定了解剖叶梦圆遗体的圣马特奥法医办公室结论。<ref>{{cite web|title=美国旧金山政府:叶梦圆非死于韩亚空难车辆碾轧|url=http://news.163.com/14/0202/01/9K1RU0D40001121M.html|author=京华时报|publisher=京华时报|accessdate=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203202355/http://news.163.com/14/0202/01/9K1RU0D40001121M.html|archive-date=2014-02-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2013-07-13/105627658540.shtml |title=韩亚空难续：江山中学夏令营31名师生回国 |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2019-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191029173119/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2013-07-13/105627658540.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

空难还造成180人受伤<ref name=c08evacuate />，其中6人伤势严重。伤者在当地的9家医院救治<ref name="2 die">{{cite news |last=Botelho |first=Greg |title=2 die, 305 survive after airliner crashes, burns at San Francisco airport |publisher=CNN |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/06/us/california-plane-incident/index.html |date=2013-07-07 |accessdate=2013-07-07 |archive-date=2013-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706195511/http://www.cnn.com/2013/07/06/us/california-plane-incident/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多数重伤的乘客都坐在飞机尾部，包括六名脊椎受损、麻痹和头部受伤的危重伤者。

== 事后 ==
